@startuml
title Sequence: Staff uploads marks
actor Staff
participant "Browser / UI" as UI
participant "Marks View" as View
participant "Result Service" as ResultSvc
database "Results DB" as DB

Staff -> UI: Open Marks Module
UI -> View: Select subject & class
View --> UI: Show entry form
Staff -> UI: Enter/Upload marks
UI -> View: Submit marks
View -> ResultSvc: Validate & calculate grade
ResultSvc -> DB: Store marks
DB --> ResultSvc: Confirm stored
ResultSvc --> View: Return status
View --> UI: Notify staff / students
@enduml
